org.js4ms.io.channel

Interface MessageKeyExtractor<MessageType>

  • Type Parameters:
    MessageType - The message object type.

    public interface MessageKeyExtractor<MessageType>
    Interface exposed by objects that extract a key value from a message. Key extractors are used to select message channels, handlers and parsers.
    Author:
    Greg Bumgardner (gbumgard)

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Object getKey(MessageType message)
      Returns a value derived from one or more attributes of a message.
